: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">中标单位收到中标通知书后，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;30</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">日内到<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标人}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">签订合同。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">招标人：<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标人}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">招标代理机构：<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标代理机构}</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">招投标监管机构：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">${监标人单位}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">中标通知书生成日期</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">:<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 13.5pt;\">${中标通知书生成日期}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"></span></p><p><br/></p>', '0');
INSERT INTO `template_info` VALUES ('737562b3-3eba-4ad9-9e71-fff36e2ab665', '招标公告-工程', 'f8caf207-a325-4521-9bea-efa4ab6dd20b', '<p style=\"text-align:center;font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19pt;\">${项目名称}</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19pt;\">招标公告</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">招标条件</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">本招标项目${项目名称}，项目业主（招标人）为<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标人}，建设资金来自#{资金来源}。出资比例为，项目已具备招标条件，现对该项目的施工进行公开招标</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">项目概况与招标范围</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">${项目概况与招标范围}<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">、资格要求</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${资质要求}</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">、招标文件的获取</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">请申请人于<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标文件发售开始时间}至<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标文件发售截止时间}，每天上午9时00分至12时00分，下午14时30分至17时30分（公休日、节假日不休）在<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标文件购买地点}携带法人委托书和身份证原件和复印件报名并购买资格预审文件。在此时间、地点以外报名的将被拒绝。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">招标文件每套售价&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${招标文件售价}&nbsp;，售后不退。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.3&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">邮购招标文件的，需另加邮费每份&nbsp;50&nbsp;元人民币，招标代理机构在收到单位介绍信和邮购款后将立即以快递方式向申请人寄送招标文件，但在任何情况下，如寄送的文件迟到或者丢失招标代理机构均不对此负责。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">、投标文件的递交</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">递交投标文件截止时间为&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${投标文件递交截止时间}，地点为<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span>${投标文件递交地点}。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.2&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">逾期送达或未送达指定地点的投标文件,招标人不予受理。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">、发布公告的媒介</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">本次招标公告在${公告发布媒体}上发布。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体;\">、&nbsp;&nbsp;联系方式</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">招标人：${招标人名称}</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">地址：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">邮编：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10.5pt;\">联系人：${联系人名称}&nb